MiniMeToken.isContract (/unique_chucks/7/0x96a0599930a67f72c713e6566687960882c5f7f9.sol#555-564) is declared view but contains assembly code

MiniMeToken.claimTokens (/unique_chucks/7/0x96a0599930a67f72c713e6566687960882c5f7f9.sol#586-601) does not use the value returned by external calls:

SwarmCrowdsale.finalization (/unique_chucks/7/0x96a0599930a67f72c713e6566687960882c5f7f9.sol#1249-1252) does not use the value returned by external calls:

SwarmCrowdsale.presaleMint (/unique_chucks/7/0x96a0599930a67f72c713e6566687960882c5f7f9.sol#1186-1188) does not use the value returned by external calls:

SwarmCrowdsale.multiPresaleMint (/unique_chucks/7/0x96a0599930a67f72c713e6566687960882c5f7f9.sol#1193-1204) does not use the value returned by external calls:
	-token.mint(_toArray[i],_amtArray[i]) (/unique_chucks/7/0x96a0599930a67f72c713e6566687960882c5f7f9.sol#1203-1204)

SwarmCrowdsale.transferUnallocatedTokens (/unique_chucks/7/0x96a0599930a67f72c713e6566687960882c5f7f9.sol#1263-1272) does not use the value returned by external calls:
	-token.mint(wallet,amountToTransfer) (/unique_chucks/7/0x96a0599930a67f72c713e6566687960882c5f7f9.sol#1270-1272)

MiniMeToken.getValueAt.min (local variable @ /unique_chucks/7/0x96a0599930a67f72c713e6566687960882c5f7f9.sol#523) shadows:
	- MiniMeToken.min (function @ /unique_chucks/7/0x96a0599930a67f72c713e6566687960882c5f7f9.sol#566-568)

SwarmCrowdsale.multiPresaleMint has external calls inside a loop:
	- token.mint(_toArray[i],_amtArray[i]) (/unique_chucks/7/0x96a0599930a67f72c713e6566687960882c5f7f9.sol#1203-1204)

Reentrancy in MiniMeMintableToken.mint (/unique_chucks/7/0x96a0599930a67f72c713e6566687960882c5f7f9.sol#700-714):
	External calls:
	- generateTokens(_to,_amount) (/unique_chucks/7/0x96a0599930a67f72c713e6566687960882c5f7f9.sol#704)
	State variables written after the call(s):
	- issuedTokens (/unique_chucks/7/0x96a0599930a67f72c713e6566687960882c5f7f9.sol#713)

MiniMeVestedToken.getVestedBalance (/unique_chucks/7/0x96a0599930a67f72c713e6566687960882c5f7f9.sol#830-864) uses timestamp for comparisons
	Dangerous comparisons:
	- _currentTime < _vestingStartTime (/unique_chucks/7/0x96a0599930a67f72c713e6566687960882c5f7f9.sol#834-838)
	- _currentTime >= _vestingStartTime.add(vestingPeriodTime.mul(vestingTotalPeriods)) (/unique_chucks/7/0x96a0599930a67f72c713e6566687960882c5f7f9.sol#840-845)

Crowdsale.Crowdsale (/unique_chucks/7/0x96a0599930a67f72c713e6566687960882c5f7f9.sol#1033-1048) uses timestamp for comparisons
	Dangerous comparisons:
	- require(bool)(_startTime >= block.timestamp) (/unique_chucks/7/0x96a0599930a67f72c713e6566687960882c5f7f9.sol#1038)

Crowdsale.validPurchase (/unique_chucks/7/0x96a0599930a67f72c713e6566687960882c5f7f9.sol#1070-1079) uses timestamp for comparisons
	Dangerous comparisons:
	- withinPeriod = current >= startTime && current <= endTime (/unique_chucks/7/0x96a0599930a67f72c713e6566687960882c5f7f9.sol#1073-1076)
	- withinPeriod && nonZeroPurchase (/unique_chucks/7/0x96a0599930a67f72c713e6566687960882c5f7f9.sol#1079)

Crowdsale.hasEnded (/unique_chucks/7/0x96a0599930a67f72c713e6566687960882c5f7f9.sol#1082-1087) uses timestamp for comparisons
	Dangerous comparisons:
	- block.timestamp > endTime (/unique_chucks/7/0x96a0599930a67f72c713e6566687960882c5f7f9.sol#1086-1087)
